id: pm-d4ns
title: "Sentry PM-CLI-2B: external extension subprocess cannot resolve pm executable"
description: Investigate and correctly attribute the single handled spawnSync pm ENOENT event emitted by an external readPmItems extension command. Determine the owning package and replace PATH-dependent recursive CLI invocation with the public pm SDK or an explicit executable contract; prevent downstream extension failures from being attributed as high pm-cli core errors without hiding actionable failures.
type: Issue
status: open
priority: 1
tags[4]: "area:observability",external-integration,sdk-adoption,sentry
