updated_at: "2026-07-15T06:21:23.181Z"
author: codex-root
estimated_minutes: 120
acceptance_criteria: Identify the emitting extension/package and release; remove or harden the PATH-dependent spawnSync pm call in the owning repository; use the public SDK where appropriate; PM-CLI-2B no longer blocks the pm-cli Sentry gate; document fresh event and telemetry evidence.
